name: Mygarage
tagline: Backend code for the server run on the raspberry pi that keeps a log of garage open/close times as well as opens and closes the garage. This works with the help of ultrasonic sensors.
body:
# MyGarage Backend
Backend code for the server run on the raspberry pi that keeps a log of garage open/close times as well as opens and closes the garage. This works with the help of ultrasonic sensors.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
